---
import CourseLayout from '../layouts/CourseLayout.astro';
---

<CourseLayout title="Module 5: Quality Management" currentModule={5}>
  
  <span class="text-sky-600 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm">Topic 5 of 6</span>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mt-2 mb-8">Quality Management Plan</h1>

  <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
    
    <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">
      Quality Management (QM) isn't about getting you in trouble; it's about ensuring we deliver the best care possible. Dream Home Care LLC uses data to improve our services constantly.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">How We Measure Quality</h3>
    
    <div class="space-y-4 mb-12">
      <div class="flex items-center p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-lg border border-slate-200">
        <div class="font-bold text-sky-600 text-xl w-12 text-center">01</div>
        <div class="flex-1 px-4">
          <strong class="block text-slate-900">Annual Home Visits</strong>
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">A supervisor will visit you while you are working to observe your techniques and ensure the care plan is being followed.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-lg border border-slate-200">
        <div class="font-bold text-sky-600 text-xl w-12 text-center">02</div>
        <div class="flex-1 px-4">
          <strong class="block text-slate-900">Participant Satisfaction Surveys</strong>
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">We ask participants: "Does your worker arrive on time?" and "Do you feel safe?" Your performance is directly tied to this feedback.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-lg border border-slate-200">
        <div class="font-bold text-sky-600 text-xl w-12 text-center">03</div>
        <div class="flex-1 px-4">
          <strong class="block text-slate-900">Performance Evaluations</strong>
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">Once a year, you will receive a formal review covering your attendance, documentation accuracy, and competency skills.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-sky-50 p-8 rounded-2xl text-center">
      <h4 class="text-sky-900 font-bold text-lg mb-2">The Continuous Improvement Loop</h4>
      <p class="text-sky-800 text-sm max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        We collect data (Surveys/Incidents) → We analyze the trends → We provide training (like this course) → Service improves.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-between items-center pt-8 mt-12 border-t border-slate-200">
        <a href="/module-4" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-sky-600 font-semibold flex items-center gap-2">
            ← Previous: Policies & Procedures
        </a>
        <a href="/module-6" class="bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg flex items-center gap-2">
            Next: Fraud Prevention →
        </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</CourseLayout>